      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CORLESS DEVIOUS (1) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Has hit the frame at his last three runs, the latest finishing third (21.27) at Nowra. Good form should continue. STAR PEDRO (7) stalked the lead after a clean break from the tricky draw and went on to finish second (22.73) at Maitland in a Grade 5 over 400m. Expected to be in the finish again. TARAWI PRINGLE (6) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (17.79) from Box 3 at Richmond Straight. Has won two of five starts from this draw. Will give a great sight again. HENDRIX (2) is a last-start placegetter at this track and distance – sure to have admirers.",
